cz.zcu.validator.jdparser.api.javadocs

Class JavaDocClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.zcu.validator.jdparser.api.javadocs.AbstractJavaDoc
      • cz.zcu.validator.jdparser.api.javadocs.JavaDocClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Authorable, Commentable, Deprecateable, Seeable, Sinceable, Versionable

    public class JavaDocClass
extends AbstractJavaDoc
implements Authorable, Versionable
    Design pattern - Messenger. Represents comment of one class. In addition to standard JavaDoc element JavaDocClass can contain author and version.
    Author:
    Stepan Cais, scais@kiv.zcu.cz, 30.11.2012
